--Dinobots--

The dinobots watch as the grenades come towards them. They tried to 
jump out of the way but as they jumped the grenades exploded sending 
them into a pile beside the ark with Grimlock the only one still 
functional.

Grimlock, "Sludge, Slag, Snarl, Swoop, Thunderwing are you guys 
alright." Grimlock then looked at his comrades only to see them 
knocked out from the exploding grenades. 

One by one Grimlock carried the Dinobots into some CR Chambers aboard 
the Ark then climbed into one himself waiting for the computer to 
repair the six fallen Maximals.
